Ed Smith Stadium is a baseball field located in Sarasota , Florida . The stadium was built in 1989 and holds 7,500 people . It is the spring training home of the Cincinnati Reds ( 1997 - present ) . It is currently home of the Single - A Sarasota Reds . Ed Smith has also hosted high school and college baseball tournaments . In the spring of 2005 , a new scoreboard was installed that features animations . Outside the stadium itself there are practice fields and a large clubhouse , mainly used for the Red 's spring training camp . 